		  <div class="__pf" id="__pf"><div data-pf-type="Body" class="sc-pRgDJ fzXWJx pf-d7d6f163"><div data-pf-type="Layout" class="pf-86c4d7d6"><div data-container="false" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-12350e3f" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-e2317012 pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--2 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--4"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-0e3fd135" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--9 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--5"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-d135340e" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-f1989996"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-5bc2f198">FAQs&nbsp;<br></span></h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-d8535619"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-32e8d853">GENERAL</span></h3><div data-pf-scrolltop="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion2" class="sc-pkfPC GftoS pf-394147cb"><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-b8408874 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-d4e89719 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="a5d4e897-1934-4cb8-8088-746b1e394147" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="true" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>1. Why True Sons hair dye products?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-17887cc3 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="a5d4e897-1934-4cb8-8088-746b1e394147" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: block;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-47cbe9a1"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-b43e6df8"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-614ab43e">True Sons was developed to give guys a higher-quality alternative to cheap drugstore brands. Our innovative, patent-pending foam formula can be applied with or without mixing to achieve a subtle effect that looks natural, not fake. If you are a dye virgin, or just hate the shoe-polish look, then True Sons might be for you.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-89afa5cd accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-aceae53f accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="beaceae5-3f41-44ee-9e89-afa5cd539bac" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>2. Where can I try True Sons?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-ee5e89af accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="beaceae5-3f41-44ee-9e89-afa5cd539bac" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-41f4ee5e"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-e53f41f4"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-79beacea">True Sons is available online via TrueSons.com website and on Amazon.com. It can be delivered to your door bi-monthly or semi-annual basis in a cool, discreet packaging.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d484478f accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-d50ea34d accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="bad50ea3-4d67-410d-8ed4-84478f516784" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>3. How long does each bottle last?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-0d8ed484 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="bad50ea3-4d67-410d-8ed4-84478f516784" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-67310d8e"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-a34d6731"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-d4bad50e">True Sons is an aerosol. That means it can be reused for multiple applications over a long period of time. How much you need depends on the length of your hair and how many body parts you are dyeing. Everyone is different.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-aae3bc2a accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-f9432ea7 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="30f9432e-a765-4ba0-99aa-e3bc2a89f05b" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>4. How many applications can I get from one bottle?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-a0d9aae3 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="30f9432e-a765-4ba0-99aa-e3bc2a89f05b" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-656ba0d9"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-2ea7656b"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-df30f943">One bottle of True Sons is good for 3-4 applications for the average user.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-72da29b4 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-57d68ac8 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="0957d68a-c8be-4e1f-8f72-da29b4ec6eab" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>5. How is it different from other men’s hair dyes?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-1f0f72da accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="0957d68a-c8be-4e1f-8f72-da29b4ec6eab" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-bede1f0f"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-8ac8bede"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-620957d6">True Sons Hair Dye Foam is the first foam hair dye available in the USA for men. It’s contains oxidative dye which react when they come in contact with the air. That means it works without the addition of developer to give guys results that look gradual and natural. It can also be mixed with True Sons Dye Booster, a 20 volume cream developer, for more grey coverage.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-514c9aaf accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-005f58aa accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="45005f58-aa95-48a0-8651-4c9aaf19b6c3" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>6. How easy is the application process?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-a046514c accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="45005f58-aa95-48a0-8651-4c9aaf19b6c3" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-9578a046"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-58aa9578"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-3945005f">It’s easier than shaving. And no nicks. Click here to see a full explanation of the application process.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-44c16643 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-47868048 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="24478680-485d-4458-a644-c166438298a2" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>7. What parts of my body can I dye with True Sons?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-586644c1 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="24478680-485d-4458-a644-c166438298a2" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-5df45866"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-80485df4"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-a4244786">You can use the same True Sons foam on multiple body parts including scalp (head) hair, beard hair, chest hair and arm hair. However, True Sons cannot ever be used on your eyebrows or eyelashes. Getting dye in your eyes is extremely dangerous. Please be careful. We also have never tested True Sons on the pubic area so please don’t use it near your business district. You might give a whole new meaning to the term ‘blue balls’.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-6603fa1e accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-604c4737 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="bd604c47-3719-469b-b166-03fa1e213511" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>8. Will True Sons stain my skin?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-9bf16603 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="bd604c47-3719-469b-b166-03fa1e213511" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-19e69bf1"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-473719e6"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-c8bd604c">As with all hair dyes, there are risks of temporary staining to your skin. Read the User’s Guide attached to your monthly box to learn how to minimize staining. Again, using on the pubic area is NOT RECOMMENDED for this reason and others.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-52766ac0 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-751f700e accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="fb751f70-0ef5-480f-a852-766ac0fcdfed" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>9. Will it stain my sink and towels?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-0f685276 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="fb751f70-0ef5-480f-a852-766ac0fcdfed" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-f5380f68"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-700ef538"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-62fb751f">Yes! It will stain everything unless it is cleaned up. For the sink (and even walls) of your bathroom, we recommend thoroughly wiping down all surfaces post application. And we mean everywhere, especially light colored. We recommend using cheap, dark-colored towels to towel off. Light colors will show stains immediately.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-e1f70335 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-2bcf744b accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="b32bcf74-4b88-4577-9ae1-f7033556ed81" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>10. Can True Sons be reused for multiple applications?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-775ae1f7 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="b32bcf74-4b88-4577-9ae1-f7033556ed81" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-8875775a"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-744b8875"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-d6b32bcf">Yes! You can reuse True Sons Hair Dye Foam for multiple applications. If applied weekly, each bottle should last about a month, depending your hair length and how many areas you dye. True Sons is packaged in a hermetically sealed aerosol can which protects the oxidative dyes from reacting until you are ready to dye again.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-5d176c42 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-2043e9a2 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="562043e9-a27b-4c6b-965d-176c425b135b" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>11. How long is the process?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-6bd65d17 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="562043e9-a27b-4c6b-965d-176c425b135b" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-7b5c6bd6"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-e9a27b5c"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-64562043">We recommend applying the product for 15 minutes the first time and evaluating the results. Need more penetration? Reapply in 5-minute intervals until you reach your desired shade.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d846219c accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-ba521f4a accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="76ba521f-4ab5-40ad-b3d8-46219ca81f2a" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>12. When do I start timing?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-ad73d846 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="76ba521f-4ab5-40ad-b3d8-46219ca81f2a" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-b590ad73"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-1f4ab590"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-2976ba52">Start counting the time after all dye foam (or mixture of dye + developer) is applied to the area. And dye one area at a time, please. Don’t be greedy.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-0fb7d567 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-a437dc61 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="40a437dc-6170-490b-a50f-b7d567e0dfeb" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>13. How often should I use True Sons?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-0b650fb7 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="40a437dc-6170-490b-a50f-b7d567e0dfeb" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-70890b65"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-dc617089"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-1240a437">That’s up to you, but we recommend reapplying once or twice a week at first. Using it more often may cause irritation. Each application should not exceed 25 minutes max.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-e96ab675 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-672b2bd8 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="f7672b2b-d83a-4d20-93e9-6ab6752014f8" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>14. How often will I have to reorder?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-20d3e96a accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="f7672b2b-d83a-4d20-93e9-6ab6752014f8" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-3acd20d3"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-2bd83acd"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-25f7672b">Most guys use one can of True Sons Hair dye per month but everyone is different, based on the amount of grey, frequency of application and length of hair being treated. To get the best price, take advantage of our 6 cans in one shipment option. It saves trees for our planet and saves money for you!</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-c4c85f3b accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-23595c3f accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="4d23595c-3fb3-4c4b-91c4-c85f3b5627f0" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>15. Do I really have to do a patch test 48 hours ahead of time?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-4b51c4c8 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="4d23595c-3fb3-4c4b-91c4-c85f3b5627f0" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-b3fc4b51"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-5c3fb3fc"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-b84d2359">Yes, you really do. Allergic reactions are rare but they do happen. How many years did you wait to try dyeing? 48 more hours won’t make a difference. You have been warned!</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-5cf57156 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-b3cdc472 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="9ab3cdc4-72f5-486a-8d5c-f571569f0f3d" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>16. Should I wash my hair before applying True Sons foam?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-6acd5cf5 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="9ab3cdc4-72f5-486a-8d5c-f571569f0f3d" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-f5a86acd"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-c472f5a8"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-3c9ab3cd">Sure. But your hair should be dry when applying True Sons and you should rinse off thoroughly immediately after dyeing. Dye on your hair will continue to react for up to 24 hours post application. This means it may look a bit darker 1-2 days after application.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-9d8b9055 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-cf89110c accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="26cf8911-0ce3-4032-9c9d-8b9055d69dde" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>17. Should I shampoo after dyeing?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-32dc9d8b accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="26cf8911-0ce3-4032-9c9d-8b9055d69dde" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-e34032dc"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-110ce340"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-d926cf89">You can if you want but it is not required. Simple rinse with water until the water runs clear. Every time you shampoo your hair, you remove some of the dye. The more shampoos, the quicker you will need to reapply.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-59aa651a accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-f2e38fca accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="66f2e38f-ca5d-468f-8c59-aa651ae056c8" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>18. Are color-extending shampoos okay to use?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-8f8c59aa accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="66f2e38f-ca5d-468f-8c59-aa651ae056c8" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-5d668f8c"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-8fca5d66"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-cf66f2e3">Yes, color-extending shampoos are fine to use. They may help extend the length of time between applications. </span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-fa4995b0 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-90974cad accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="0c90974c-ad6c-4a44-98fa-4995b02293e9" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>19. What are these wipes anyway?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-4418fa49 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="0c90974c-ad6c-4a44-98fa-4995b02293e9" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-6c8a4418"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-4cad6c8a"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-3f0c9097">The wipes are specially formulated to remove stains from skin. It’s normal to see some staining. This usually goes away after a day. To reduce the risk of staining, remove any foam that gets on the hairline during application to prevent exposure. Some guys also choose to line their beard or hair line with Vaseline or Chapstick to create an impenetrable barrier that protects the exposed skin from the dye. </span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-52b082da accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-fccc78fa accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="69fccc78-fa45-49b6-9a52-b082dacd2e8e" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>20. I used to dye my hair with a drugstore brand. How can I match that shade?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-b65a52b0 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="69fccc78-fa45-49b6-9a52-b082dacd2e8e" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-4539b65a"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-78fa4539"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-7169fccc">Click here for a chart that we created to help steer you right. When we developed our line of shades, we purchased every single shade offered by some of our competitors. Even we couldn’t tell the difference between some of them, the results were so subtle. We decided that our shade line is all you really need to get good results. </span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-c41f07cc accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-82c871d1 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="2682c871-d10c-4f6d-93c4-1f07ccab1329" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>21. How do I find my perfect shade?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-6d93c41f accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="2682c871-d10c-4f6d-93c4-1f07ccab1329" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-0c3f6d93"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-71d10c3f"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-492682c8">Ask your barber, partner or a close friend you trust to not give away your secret! Then try one of our shades. If it’s not right, then you can edit your shade choice at least one week before your next shipment. </span></p></div></div></div></div><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-29031386"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-ab132903">ORDERING QUESTIONS</span></h3><div data-pf-scrolltop="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion2" class="sc-pkfPC GftoS pf-d6f06165"><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-a7d51247 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-9d0b0f2e accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="449d0b0f-2e91-4dd8-99fc-ea3df3530f8d" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>1. Can I change my shade whenever I want? </button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-496cef7f accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="449d0b0f-2e91-4dd8-99fc-ea3df3530f8d" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-0935970c"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-0f2e917d"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-15888485">You can change the shade you receive for each shipment by changing your account settings one week before your next ship date.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-151da844 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-219d9c30 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="3d219d9c-30d4-49cd-9e15-1da8448b86fc" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>2. Can I change the frequency whenever I want?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-cd5e151d accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="3d219d9c-30d4-49cd-9e15-1da8448b86fc" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-d419cd5e"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-9c30d419"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-923d219d">You can choose between bi-monthly or semi-annual shipments of True Sons. To change your delivery frequency, log into your account.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-47cf7929 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-136d2ae5 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="7a136d2a-e5e7-4670-8347-cf7929cff5d9" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>3. Can I cancel or edit frequency whenever I want?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-704347cf accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="7a136d2a-e5e7-4670-8347-cf7929cff5d9" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-e7567043"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-2ae5e756"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-447a136d">Yes. Any plan changes, including cancellations, must be received one full week before your next shipment date. You can also pause or skip a shipment by logging into your account, going to Manage Subscription, click ORDER # and adjust each shipment to your liking.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-e427a986 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-0a63c5f8 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="e90a63c5-f8fe-415e-a8e4-27a986c8336e" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>4. How do I cancel?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-5ea8e427 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="e90a63c5-f8fe-415e-a8e4-27a986c8336e" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-fe415ea8"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-c5f8fe41"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-f6e90a63">To cancel your subscription, send us a request here: https://truesons.com/pages/contact Any plan changes, including cancellations, must be received one full week before your next shipment date.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-5d3c9012 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-7c032851 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="2a7c0328-51b7-4d22-955d-3c9012ac01d9" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>5. How long will it take my order to arrive?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-22555d3c accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="2a7c0328-51b7-4d22-955d-3c9012ac01d9" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-b73d2255"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-2851b73d"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-7b2a7c03">True Sons usually ships out new orders within 1 business day. It can take up to 5-7 business days to be delivered, as our aerosol cans contain pressurized gas that can only ship ground. We are not able to offer expedited, air, or international shipping at this time. We are able to ship to PO and APO boxes.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d8e62842 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-70b9f3e7 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="a870b9f3-e76e-4503-8ed8-e6284221a4fb" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>6. Where do you ship?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-030ed8e6 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="a870b9f3-e76e-4503-8ed8-e6284221a4fb" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-6ec5030e"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-f3e76ec5"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-bfa870b9">We currently ship only within the continental United States only. Sorry, Hawaii, Alaska, and Guam!</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-63d6f839 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-2b38ea96 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="602b38ea-969a-484d-8f63-d6f83978679d" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>7. Can I make a one time purchase?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-4d8f63d6 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="602b38ea-969a-484d-8f63-d6f83978679d" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-9aa84d8f"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-ea969aa8"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-df602b38">True Sons is available in limited quantities, so we can only make it available to people who subscribe. However, if you aren’t completely happy with your purchase, you can cancel at least one week before the next shipment. You can also or skip a shipment by logging into your account, going to Manage Subscription, click ORDER # and adjust each shipment as you wish.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-ce6b597f accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-7810b4c0 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="4e7810b4-c000-41fe-b4ce-6b597f997ab6" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>8. Can I purchase True Sons at a retail location?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-feb4ce6b accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="4e7810b4-c000-41fe-b4ce-6b597f997ab6" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-0061feb4"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-b4c00061"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-fd4e7810">Not yet. True Sons is only available online at TrueSons.com and Amazon.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-4bff0f37 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-f31c9dae accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="8cf31c9d-ae1b-4251-af4b-ff0f37ecba41" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>9. Can I return product?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-516f4bff accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="8cf31c9d-ae1b-4251-af4b-ff0f37ecba41" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-1b72516f"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-9dae1b72"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-d58cf31c">True Sons does not offer refunds for any reason. We will happily exchange unopened and unused bottles for a different shade.</span></p></div></div></div></div><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-41ab71b6"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-ecba41ab">PRODUCT SPECIFIC</span></h3><div data-pf-scrolltop="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion2" class="sc-pkfPC GftoS pf-6f0b97f8"><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d32cf54d accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-b8eba827 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="5eb8eba8-2784-4222-911d-e14024ba1127" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>1. Can women use True Sons products?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-a1ead3f3 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="5eb8eba8-2784-4222-911d-e14024ba1127" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-2e374866"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-a82784c2"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-ab8ddce9">Of course! Although True Sons was made specifically for men, women can use our products as well to achieve a natural look. However, we are only available in a limited number of shades.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-4d607e38 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-60a3d753 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="6060a3d7-5328-47c5-954d-607e383ce56f" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>2. Where is it made?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-c5954d60 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="6060a3d7-5328-47c5-954d-607e383ce56f" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-28a7c595"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-d75328a7"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-ab6060a3">We proudly manufacture and fill our product within the USA. Some ingredients and materials that go into the product are sourced outside the USA.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-9964a2fd accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-f5c812d1 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="04f5c812-d179-4a9e-a099-64a2fd4a30df" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i> 3. Does True Sons test on animals?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-9ee09964 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="04f5c812-d179-4a9e-a099-64a2fd4a30df" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-796a9ee0"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-12d1796a"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-6b04f5c8">True Sons is cruelty-free. We do not test our products on animals. We will not sell into countries that require animal testing. Please do not use True Sons on your dog or cat. If we find out, we will cancel your subscription!</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-a1a107cf accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-bcd9b4e3 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="ddbcd9b4-e36d-45f9-b6a1-a107cfd55669" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>4. Will the color wash off or fade?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-f976a1a1 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="ddbcd9b4-e36d-45f9-b6a1-a107cfd55669" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-6d75f976"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-b4e36d75"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-11ddbcd9">Excess exposure to the sun, or chlorine from a swimming pool will risk your color fade faster. Shampooing often also speeds fading. In such cases, simply re-apply True Sons. You can also use a color-extending shampoo, but be careful to make sure you don’t have any skin staining when you apply color-extending shampoos.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-d4fd636f accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-543a9982 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="91543a99-8258-4742-99d4-fd636f733917" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>5. I cannot remember what shade I ordered?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-4299d4fd accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="91543a99-8258-4742-99d4-fd636f733917" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-58474299"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-99825847"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-6a91543a">That’s simple, just look at the bottom of the can to find the shade name, or login to your account and see your order history.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-pJipy mZVAk pf-8644cd68 accordion__item" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content.Wrapper"><button type="button" class="sc-pBlxj gYSgcm pf-0f81d917 accordion__header pf-anchor" data-header-id="d70f81d9-17a4-4205-bc86-44cd686effdc" data-action="accordion2" data-preopen="false" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="icon_position accordion__arrow fa fa-chevron-right"></i>6. What are the ingredients in True Sons hair dye?</button><div class="sc-qYUWV exYsxy pf-05fc8644 accordion__content" mode="view" data-id="d70f81d9-17a4-4205-bc86-44cd686effdc" data-pf-type="Accordion2.Content" style="display: none;"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-oUbqx bgMQOP pf-a4c205fc"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-d917a4c2"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-06d70f81">Our shade formulas vary, but here is a sample ingredient list of one shade. Should you have questions about other shades, please contact support@truesons.com.
